            <description><![CDATA[
                            <h2>New Features</h2>
                            <ul>
                                <li>Adds localizations for Japanese (thanks, Nob!), German, and English (United Kingdom)</li>
                            </ul>
                            <h2>Fixes and Improvements</h2>
                            <ul>
                                <li>Adds tooltips to the goal checkboxes and toolbar buttons</li>
                                <li>Text fields are now as wide as their contents, making it easier to reorder your goals</li>
                                <li>Fixes an issue where an untitled goal would remain after quitting while a new goal was being added</li>
                                <li>Fixes an issue where updates on the Express channel could not be found</li>
                                <li>Fixes a few minor issues in the interface</li>
                                <li>Includes minor updates behind the scenes</li>
                            </ul>
                            <h2>Known Issues</h2>
                            <ul>
                                <li>Scrolling the goal list may not work as intended and exhibit some “stuttering.” We are working on a solution and apologize for any inconvenience.</li>
                            </ul>
							]]></description>
